 Conclusion
The Smart Me Fashion Assistant is an innovative AI-based solution that simplifies outfit selection by analyzing clothing images and providing intelligent recommendations. By incorporating budget considerations and personalization, the system enhances user convenience and promotes smart fashion choices. This project demonstrates the practical application of AI in everyday life.

